{"nodes": [{"id": "draft6_0_research_north_star_th_4_signal", "label": "North-star 4 \u2014 Learning Signal / Correctness as Feeling", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "draft6.0\\research\\north-star\\th\\4-signal.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "The deepest idea: correctness is a self-generated, learnable feeling (not an external label); the field calls it prediction-error/surprise minimization, and Active Inference explains self-verification."}, {"id": "draft6_0_research_north_star_th_4_signal_active_inference", "label": "Free Energy Principle / Active Inference", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "draft6.0\\research\\north-star\\th\\4-signal.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Friston: minimize variational free energy; the home theory for 'correctness is a feeling' \u2014 grounded (measured vs real input, can't lie for long) and explains self-verification as epistemic action; F ~ SCFF prediction error already in the circuit."}, {"id": "draft6_0_research_north_star_th_4_signal_curiosity_icm", "label": "Curiosity / ICM / compression progress", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "draft6.0\\research\\north-star\\th\\4-signal.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Pathak 2017 / Schmidhuber: prediction error as reward, computed in learned feature space (not pixels); the twin of the correctness feeling \u2014 drives 'go learn more'."}, {"id": "draft6_0_research_north_star_th_4_signal_world_models", "label": "World Models / Dreamer", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "draft6.0\\research\\north-star\\th\\4-signal.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Ha & Schmidhuber 2018 / Hafner: V+M+C, train in imagination; 'thinking' = running the world model internally; one organ M plans awake and replays asleep."}, {"id": "draft6_0_research_north_star_th_4_signal_actor_critic", "label": "Learnable critic (actor-critic)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "draft6.0\\research\\north-star\\th\\4-signal.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Sutton & Barto / A3C / PPO: the feeling-of-correct should be a small learnable model trained by TD error on grounding events, sitting beside main compute; V(s) ~ negative F."}, {"id": "draft6_0_research_north_star_th_4_signal_correctness_feeling", "label": "Correctness as a self-generated feeling", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "draft6.0\\research\\north-star\\th\\4-signal.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "The project's deepest thesis; = collapse of prediction-error/free-energy on settling, grounded against sensory input, implemented as a learnable critic, verified via epistemic actions on a world model."}, {"id": "draft6_0_research_north_star_th_4_signal_tap_drift_seed", "label": "Class-direction tap-drift gate (planted seed)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "draft6.0\\research\\north-star\\th\\4-signal.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Phase-8.2 built & validated sig_tap_drift_direction (leads labeled error ~8 steps, spine-clean, matches DriftLens) but NOT deployed \u2014 frozen loop uses DDM error-EMA; parked as a FUTURE SEPARATE recurrent-halt experiment, not a retrofit."}], "edges": [{"source": "draft6_0_research_north_star_th_4_signal", "target": "draft6_0_research_north_star_th_4_signal_active_inference", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "draft6.0\\research\\north-star\\th\\4-signal.md", "source_location": null